profile: At Fusion Glassworks, art and architecture come together. Our skilled designers will work closely with you to create unique and beautiful glass panels to suit your individual style. Using large scale state-of-the-art techniques, we strive to produce superior quality products at affordable prices. Every unit comes with a 10-year thermal seal warranty and is hand-made in our top-of-the-line facility to ensure that each unit has been triple-glazed properly. Nothing brings warmth and character into a home like the subtle beauty of stained glass. Come visit our showroom or call us for a free estimate. We can also arrange to come to your house for a free consultation.
specialities: decorative glass panels, wrought iron, glass showers, vanity & bar tops, stained glass, cabinet inserts, slumped glass, religious themes.
